Sentencas: BaCe0.9Yb0.1O3- was prepared via the sol-gel method using zirconium nitrate, ytterbium trioxide, cerium nitrate and barium acetate as raw materials.
Titulo: Yb-Doped BaCeO3 and Its Composite Electrolyte for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Subsequently, it reacted with the binary NaCl similar to KCl salt to obtain BaCe0.9Yb0.1O3--NaCl similar to KCl composite electrolyte.
Titulo: Yb-Doped BaCeO3 and Its Composite Electrolyte for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The structure, morphology, conductivity and fuel cell performance of the obtained samples were investigated.
Titulo: Yb-Doped BaCeO3 and Its Composite Electrolyte for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscope (SEM) images showed that BaCe0.9Yb0.1O3- and NaCl similar to KCl combined with each other to form a homogeneous 3-D reticulated structure.
Titulo: Yb-Doped BaCeO3 and Its Composite Electrolyte for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The highest power density and conductivity of BaCe0.9Yb0.1O3--NaCl similar to KCl was 393 mWcm(-2)
